WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 14=

01:43.990 --> 01:46.780
(Grace Garden)

01:46.790 --> 01:47.640
Maybe

01:47.640 --> 01:48.550
some rare treasures

01:48.550 --> 01:49.550
will be on display.

01:53.340 --> 01:54.750
I've heard Master Yili'er

01:54.750 --> 01:56.190
has a remarkable skill

01:56.470 --> 01:58.500
for identifying gold and treasures.

01:59.220 --> 02:01.190
If he identifies anything authentic,

02:01.500 --> 02:03.390
he'll even spend a fortune to buy it.

02:04.140 --> 02:05.390
This is my family heirloom.

02:05.620 --> 02:06.470
How I wish

02:06.470 --> 02:08.350
I could be so fortunate.

02:09.670 --> 02:11.180
I wonder if Master Yili'er

02:11.180 --> 02:12.180
will teach others.

02:12.420 --> 02:14.110
It would be even better

02:14.110 --> 02:14.950
if he could teach me.

02:16.740 --> 02:17.900
It's starting. Let's get in.

02:18.460 --> 02:19.300
Come on.

02:21.300 --> 02:22.140
Your Grace.

02:23.110 --> 02:23.950
The show begins.

02:27.990 --> 02:29.020
Master Yili'er is here.

02:30.620 --> 02:31.600
There you are, Master.

02:31.660 --> 02:32.510
Master,

02:32.510 --> 02:33.900
take a look at my treasure.

02:33.900 --> 02:34.740
Look at mine.

02:34.750 --> 02:36.350
This is my family heirloom.

02:38.550 --> 02:39.420
My dear guests,

02:40.110 --> 02:41.620
you've all come with your treasures.

02:41.950 --> 02:44.020
I'll identify them one by one.

02:44.440 --> 02:45.300
All right.

02:45.300 --> 02:46.460
If the treasure is genuine,

02:46.740 --> 02:48.140
you'll get 1,000 pieces of gold.

02:50.390 --> 02:52.020
But if it's fake,

02:52.390 --> 02:53.900
it'll be destroyed right here.

02:54.070 --> 02:54.910
What?

02:55.620 --> 02:56.460
Destroyed?

02:56.460 --> 02:57.580
Mine is real. I'm not afraid.

02:57.580 --> 02:58.420
- Right.
- Go ahead.

03:03.020 --> 03:03.900
So many dignitaries.

03:05.270 --> 03:06.550
Peerless in Youzhou, indeed.

03:15.300 --> 03:16.300
If you smell like this,

03:16.990 --> 03:18.270
even the best nose

03:18.270 --> 03:19.230
will no longer work.

03:21.510 --> 03:22.420
Go to the woodshed

03:22.420 --> 03:23.270
and smell the firewood

03:23.700 --> 03:24.550
to restore this sense.

03:25.860 --> 03:27.390
You mortals are such a hassle.

03:31.100 --> 03:31.950
It seems

03:31.950 --> 03:33.740
you're here to collect scents

03:33.990 --> 03:35.070
instead of finding the Lord

03:35.230 --> 03:36.230
of Jiling Temple.

03:39.070 --> 03:40.620
Can you sense if Song Xingyu is here?

03:46.670 --> 03:47.990
He stole the Glazed Pagoda,

03:47.990 --> 03:48.830
a magic tool,

03:49.300 --> 03:50.950
to evade my spiritual perception.

03:52.230 --> 03:53.670
Then how will you lure him out?

03:58.180 --> 04:00.070
Yili'er made a deal with Song Xingyu.

04:00.950 --> 04:02.420
But now he wants you.

04:03.300 --> 04:04.950
So they've grown estranged.

04:05.740 --> 04:06.580
Yili'er

04:07.140 --> 04:08.670
is the one we need to crack.

04:17.060 --> 04:18.300
What a peculiar smell.

04:25.060 --> 04:25.900
Precious sword.

04:28.150 --> 04:28.990
Sword.

04:29.990 --> 04:31.030
It's pretty good.

04:34.710 --> 04:35.550
This sword...

04:36.060 --> 04:37.590
I'll offer 5,000 pieces of gold.

04:37.590 --> 04:39.300
- 5,000 pieces?
- 5,000?

04:40.230 --> 04:41.990
Now destroy

04:42.470 --> 04:43.500
all the counterfeits!

04:43.820 --> 04:44.940
What?

04:44.940 --> 04:45.820
All of them?

04:45.820 --> 04:46.660
Really?

04:46.670 --> 04:47.860
They can't all be fake, huh?

04:47.860 --> 04:49.670
But...

04:49.670 --> 04:51.110
It doesn't look fake at all.

04:56.860 --> 04:58.110
It was really smashed.

05:00.940 --> 05:01.910
And even this one?

05:07.610 --> 05:08.460
Again.

05:08.470 --> 05:09.620
So much gold.

05:10.820 --> 05:11.660
This is too much.

05:12.260 --> 05:13.300
Thank you, Master.

05:14.230 --> 05:15.420
Can you even move that?

05:15.740 --> 05:16.620
You've made a fortune.

05:16.620 --> 05:18.150
This man is truly lucky.

05:18.150 --> 05:18.990
Congratulations.

05:20.300 --> 05:22.380
A genuine item
will be worth a hundredfold.

05:22.620 --> 05:24.060
A counterfeit will be destroyed.

05:24.420 --> 05:26.180
It's a huge gamble, indeed.

05:26.860 --> 05:27.700
Master.

05:28.860 --> 05:29.700
Master, Master.

05:30.670 --> 05:31.510
This is mine.

05:31.670 --> 05:32.710
Look at mine.

05:38.940 --> 05:40.230
Master, please take a look.

05:41.860 --> 05:42.700
Look.

05:42.990 --> 05:45.230
Is this jade vase

05:45.500 --> 05:46.990
genuine or fake?

05:47.990 --> 05:49.350
Where did you get it?

05:49.820 --> 05:50.670
At a young age,

05:50.670 --> 05:52.990
my grandfather got this jade piece

05:53.260 --> 05:55.110
from a renowned master

05:55.300 --> 05:56.150
when he traveled

05:56.150 --> 05:57.000
with my ancestors.

05:57.000 --> 05:57.860
Yili'er is just

05:58.260 --> 05:59.550
what they say he is.

05:59.910 --> 06:00.940
Not exactly.

06:01.500 --> 06:03.420
Calm down and see for yourself.

06:03.660 --> 06:05.500
How much is it worth?

06:05.670 --> 06:07.260
Antiques oppose wind energy.

06:07.710 --> 06:09.230
If the wisps of wind can tightly

06:09.230 --> 06:10.380
connect with the antique,

06:10.620 --> 06:12.420
it means it's real.

06:12.940 --> 06:13.820
Conversely,

06:13.820 --> 06:14.660
it's fake.

06:19.790 --> 06:20.940
It's...

06:22.350 --> 06:23.190
What's this?

06:23.860 --> 06:25.230
A drop of water falls on the jade.

06:25.710 --> 06:27.380
If it stays as a dewdrop

06:27.620 --> 06:28.910
without dispersing,

06:29.150 --> 06:29.990
it's real jade.

06:31.350 --> 06:32.710
This item doesn't match.

06:32.860 --> 06:34.150
It doesn't?

06:34.470 --> 06:35.620
But that is genuine.

06:36.590 --> 06:38.620
So we're watching a show

06:39.150 --> 06:40.550
"a deceitful substitution."

06:43.350 --> 06:44.470
Destroy it now.

06:44.710 --> 06:45.550
Destroy? No.

06:46.910 --> 06:48.060
You can't destroy it.

06:48.740 --> 06:49.670
Don't listen to him.

06:49.910 --> 06:50.820
Hey.

06:50.820 --> 06:51.660
Yeah.

06:52.180 --> 06:53.710
There's no way this is fake.

06:56.790 --> 06:57.820
Oh no. I...

06:57.820 --> 06:58.710
Move, move.

06:59.030 --> 07:00.350
Get out of the way.

07:00.350 --> 07:01.230
What are you doing?

07:02.500 --> 07:03.470
Check mine, please.

07:03.620 --> 07:04.910
It's from the previous dynasty.

07:05.180 --> 07:06.300
Look at this.

07:06.550 --> 07:07.940
- Previous dynasty?
- Looks nice.

07:08.150 --> 07:09.030
Nice, isn't it?

07:12.470 --> 07:13.820
It's finely crafted

07:15.110 --> 07:16.180
with smooth lines.

07:16.350 --> 07:17.230
That's right.

07:18.260 --> 07:19.710
Sadly, it's too thick and heavy.

07:20.180 --> 07:21.910
Not from the previous dynasty.

07:23.150 --> 07:25.150
It's a current forgery.

07:25.380 --> 07:26.590
There's no way

07:26.860 --> 07:28.180
this is an antique.

07:30.740 --> 07:31.710
According to the rules,

07:32.300 --> 07:34.260
a fake must be destroyed here.

07:41.060 --> 07:41.940
Since it's a fake,

07:43.300 --> 07:44.420
why not sell it to me?

07:45.940 --> 07:46.790
Who is she?

08:12.030 --> 08:12.870
What is that?

08:15.030 --> 08:16.740
Why does it give off a strange scent?

08:26.500 --> 08:27.940
It's a bracelet made of agarwood.

08:28.350 --> 08:29.190
Very precious.

08:30.470 --> 08:31.310
Miss, it's my honor

08:32.020 --> 08:33.190
to have you live here.

08:34.070 --> 08:35.020
Take this

08:35.190 --> 08:37.590
as a welcoming gift.

08:42.830 --> 08:43.780
People usually

08:43.780 --> 08:46.310
have a deal with newly shaped spirits

08:46.950 --> 08:48.070
as their servants.

08:48.710 --> 08:50.990
I've never seen anyone

08:51.470 --> 08:53.500
who has a deal
with such a powerful spirit.

08:54.780 --> 08:56.310
Who says I'm his servant?

08:56.990 --> 08:58.740
I'm the master and he's the servant.

08:58.740 --> 08:59.900
I command him.

09:09.350 --> 09:10.190
Miss,

09:10.500 --> 09:11.540
if you don't mind,

09:12.350 --> 09:14.110
will you hand him over

09:14.310 --> 09:15.740
to me?

09:16.430 --> 09:17.860
Name your price.

09:22.590 --> 09:23.660
You're carrying the token

09:23.660 --> 09:24.990
of the Lord of Jiling Temple.

09:25.350 --> 09:26.540
How dare you want another one?

09:27.020 --> 09:28.540
I don't dare to let my spirit

09:28.540 --> 09:29.950
snatch his servant.

09:30.860 --> 09:32.310
How do you know?

09:36.500 --> 09:38.020
No wonder you said

09:38.020 --> 09:39.260
your spirit was disobedient.

09:40.070 --> 09:41.110
Have you also heard that?

09:42.110 --> 09:43.740
The Lord of Jiling Temple is in trouble.

09:44.500 --> 09:45.710
Are you going to abandon him?

09:50.070 --> 09:51.900
It seems you don't know.

09:53.190 --> 09:54.500
He offended the Sovereign

09:54.830 --> 09:56.310
and fled to the Mortal World.

09:57.230 --> 09:58.140
Now,

09:58.140 --> 09:59.430
he has been tracked down.

10:00.710 --> 10:01.710
I think

10:10.020 --> 10:11.260
if he gets caught,

10:11.620 --> 10:12.950
he should be executed immediately.

10:13.590 --> 10:15.110
Otherwise, if he escapes again

10:15.620 --> 10:16.540
or if he

10:16.540 --> 10:17.900
gets locked up for centuries,

10:18.540 --> 10:20.070
he won't answer when you call him.

10:20.620 --> 10:22.310
And you can't casually get a new spirit.

10:23.310 --> 10:24.900
Then your life

10:29.070 --> 10:29.910
will pass by quickly.

10:36.830 --> 10:37.670
Miss,

10:38.140 --> 10:40.230
if I end up having no spirit,

10:40.780 --> 10:43.070
will you give me yours?

10:45.470 --> 10:46.830
What will you give me in return?

10:47.380 --> 10:48.260
What do you want?

11:52.020 --> 11:52.860
Who's that?

12:02.740 --> 12:03.590
Song Xingyu?

12:03.780 --> 12:06.900
(Song Xingyu, Lord of Jiling Temple)

12:09.710 --> 12:11.350
Greetings, My Lord.

12:13.230 --> 12:14.860
Why am I losing control of my mouth?

12:19.190 --> 12:20.190
Look, My Lord.

12:20.350 --> 12:21.430
These are the treasures

12:21.430 --> 12:22.470
I've collected for you.

12:22.660 --> 12:24.140
They're sparkling and valuable.

12:39.590 --> 12:40.430
Tell me.

12:41.230 --> 12:42.620
When stealing during the day,

12:43.500 --> 12:45.230
did you see a woman with a spirit?

12:47.380 --> 12:48.590
I'm very familiar with them.

12:48.870 --> 12:49.710
Do you mean

12:49.710 --> 12:51.380
the spirit holding a sword?

12:51.860 --> 12:53.140
Does the woman have spirit power?

12:54.240 --> 12:55.080
No.

12:55.080 --> 12:56.110
She's a mere mortal.

13:00.830 --> 13:03.310
So, Fang Chang didn't lie.

13:08.540 --> 13:09.620
How powerful is the spirit

13:09.830 --> 13:10.780
by her side?

13:12.620 --> 13:13.830
I can't tell

13:14.070 --> 13:14.990
how powerful he is.

13:15.540 --> 13:17.190
But he can use the mortal's sword.

13:17.660 --> 13:18.780
That sword is powerful.

13:20.500 --> 13:22.140
Let's do something to separate them.

13:23.380 --> 13:24.220
My Lord,

13:24.830 --> 13:26.230
can you kill that spirit

13:26.590 --> 13:27.710
and give me his sword?

13:27.950 --> 13:28.790
Get lost!

13:29.430 --> 13:31.020
Who is the Lord, you or me?

13:32.020 --> 13:33.830
How dare you order me around?

13:34.110 --> 13:35.590
I'm sorry, My Lord.

13:35.590 --> 13:37.590
I'll go figure out how to separate them.

13:37.590 --> 13:38.430
No need.

13:38.830 --> 13:40.190
I'll find a way to separate them.

13:40.420 --> 13:41.260
By then,

13:41.260 --> 13:42.620
you just hold that spirit off.

13:42.990 --> 13:43.830
Yes.

13:43.830 --> 13:45.380
If you manage to snatch the sword,

13:45.740 --> 13:46.860
bring it back to me.

13:54.660 --> 13:55.500
Yes.

14:00.540 --> 14:02.310
This Gold-threaded Glove

14:02.900 --> 14:05.260
can block the aura of magic tools.

14:06.430 --> 14:08.860
Wear it to get the sword.

14:11.070 --> 14:11.910
Yes.

14:16.380 --> 14:17.220
My Lord,

14:18.380 --> 14:19.620
can I have that tower?

14:19.990 --> 14:20.900
Get out!

14:20.900 --> 14:21.740
Yes.

14:38.190 --> 14:40.020
- My ball.
- Young Master, don't go.

14:40.020 --> 14:41.470
Don't go there. Come back.

14:41.470 --> 14:42.310
Young Master.

14:42.590 --> 14:43.470
Is he all right?

14:43.470 --> 14:44.590
- Dangerous.
- Is he fine?

14:44.590 --> 14:45.430
Be very careful.

14:45.430 --> 14:46.290
My ball.

14:46.290 --> 14:47.160
Let's go.

14:48.740 --> 14:49.950
I was really freaked out.

14:50.430 --> 14:51.950
Nothing must happen to Young Master.

15:01.260 --> 15:02.950
You know what? After the fete was over,

15:03.260 --> 15:05.020
Master had a stunning woman

15:05.020 --> 15:05.950
stay here.

15:05.950 --> 15:07.740
Maybe she'll be his new bride.

15:08.020 --> 15:09.620
Four ladies can't help feeling restless.

15:09.780 --> 15:10.650
Just now,

15:10.650 --> 15:11.860
I saw them head aggressively

15:11.860 --> 15:12.780
toward the woodshed

15:12.990 --> 15:14.140
to give her a hard time.

15:15.380 --> 15:16.250
Looks like Master

15:16.250 --> 15:17.140
wants another child.

15:18.470 --> 15:19.380
Because his children,

15:19.380 --> 15:20.430
male or female,

15:20.430 --> 15:21.350
always die young.

15:23.710 --> 15:24.710
People are gossiping.

15:25.140 --> 15:27.110
These years, Master has been wealthier.

15:27.470 --> 15:28.500
But among his children,

15:28.780 --> 15:29.660
only Young Master Luda

15:29.660 --> 15:30.500
grew up to adulthood.

15:31.070 --> 15:31.990
(Luda?)

15:31.990 --> 15:34.620
Maybe it's a curse.

15:35.900 --> 15:37.780
Young Master Luda
went to the capital at ten

15:37.780 --> 15:38.660
and never returned.

15:39.430 --> 15:40.350
Master

15:40.350 --> 15:41.950
doesn't seem to want him back.

16:15.950 --> 16:16.790
Simu.

16:17.780 --> 16:18.710
Yili'er's son is Luda,

16:18.710 --> 16:19.550
a senior official

16:20.110 --> 16:20.950
in the Capital.

16:21.350 --> 16:22.230
Then?

16:22.230 --> 16:23.310
Another friend of yours?

16:24.430 --> 16:25.910
I'm not worthy of a friend like that.

16:26.950 --> 16:28.470
He's the High Priest's favorite pupil,

16:29.020 --> 16:30.020
Young Priest Luda.

16:30.950 --> 16:32.460
He's very likely to be High Priest.

16:33.370 --> 16:34.230
In the Chong Court,

16:34.230 --> 16:35.070
everybody knows him.

16:41.500 --> 16:42.900
That explains

16:43.740 --> 16:45.020
why Yili'er can have

16:45.300 --> 16:46.140
so many treasures

16:46.140 --> 16:46.980
from the royal court.

16:47.860 --> 16:48.700
You think

16:49.110 --> 16:50.660
he's also involved in this?

16:51.500 --> 16:52.340
I don't think so.

16:53.140 --> 16:54.230
He scorns such things.

16:55.350 --> 16:56.860
Have mercy upon us.

16:57.140 --> 16:58.860
Have mercy upon us.

16:59.070 --> 17:00.500
There's confusion.

17:01.110 --> 17:01.990
There's confusion.

17:01.990 --> 17:03.140
He looks very ethereal.

17:04.430 --> 17:05.870
It's said to be

17:07.230 --> 17:09.740
the most important gift
for becoming a priest.

17:15.260 --> 17:16.740
What are you going to do

17:17.300 --> 17:18.390
to Yili'er and Song Xingyu?

17:20.230 --> 17:21.580
Now that I'm here,

17:22.300 --> 17:23.830
I'll wait until they come to me.

17:26.740 --> 17:27.580
How arrogant.

17:56.660 --> 18:00.380
(Jiang Ai, Left Hand of the Void)

18:26.260 --> 18:27.870
Thinking of sending Simu

18:27.870 --> 18:28.910
another present?

18:30.190 --> 18:31.390
If you keep waiting,

18:31.390 --> 18:33.190
you'll be like a waiting husband.

18:34.060 --> 18:35.500
Her Grace has been away for so long.

18:35.740 --> 18:36.990
Without constraints,

18:36.990 --> 18:38.260
you seem pretty carefree.

18:39.340 --> 18:41.430
Simu has never constrained me.

18:41.820 --> 18:42.780
But look at you.

18:43.190 --> 18:44.390
When Her Grace is away,

18:44.390 --> 18:45.390
you're in charge.

18:45.390 --> 18:47.060
Shouldn't you feel happier?

18:47.580 --> 18:49.470
Why are you acting like a resentful man?

18:53.340 --> 18:54.430
Oh, I see.

18:55.780 --> 18:59.020
Her Grace has been
in the Mortal World for so long.

19:00.540 --> 19:02.710
Is she seeing another man?

19:04.340 --> 19:06.540
Oh, you must be heartbroken.

19:07.740 --> 19:08.820
Hitting a nerve?

19:09.580 --> 19:11.710
You called me over for a discussion.

19:15.870 --> 19:17.260
Since you have so much free time,

19:17.820 --> 19:18.670
why don't you

19:18.670 --> 19:20.020
authorize the fund request

19:20.020 --> 19:20.860
for two billion spirit stones?

19:21.060 --> 19:22.870
Her Grace approved it before she left.

19:23.580 --> 19:25.500
When are you going to stop stalling?

19:27.820 --> 19:28.820
I suddenly remembered

19:28.950 --> 19:30.260
I had work to do.

19:30.780 --> 19:31.670
I should go.

19:47.020 --> 19:47.990
Go to the Mortal World.

19:48.540 --> 19:49.780
If Her Grace has a problem,

19:50.230 --> 19:51.430
inform me immediately.

19:51.580 --> 19:52.420
- Yes.
- Yes.

20:01.710 --> 20:02.630
Spring water ginseng.

20:08.780 --> 20:09.620
Xiling mutton.

20:14.910 --> 20:15.780
North Sea snow lotus.

20:18.470 --> 20:19.470
That's so you.

20:19.990 --> 20:21.150
After just a few days,

20:21.340 --> 20:22.780
you can identify food with clarity.

20:23.150 --> 20:24.300
So, you wrote a note

20:24.300 --> 20:25.670
and asked me to have the servants

20:25.670 --> 20:26.580
prepare this, right?

20:27.060 --> 20:27.900
Exactly.

20:28.190 --> 20:29.030
I'm just curious

20:29.190 --> 20:30.260
about how well you're doing

20:30.260 --> 20:31.390
with your sense of smell.

20:37.150 --> 20:38.260
It's me, Miss.

20:39.190 --> 20:40.820
May I come in and talk to you?

20:42.260 --> 20:43.340
This is your house.

20:43.870 --> 20:44.740
Don't be so formal.

20:48.340 --> 20:49.180
Miss He,

20:49.430 --> 20:51.390
I have a favor to ask of you.

21:25.430 --> 21:26.390
What favor?

21:28.820 --> 21:29.820
My son Luda

21:30.230 --> 21:31.070
lived in the Capital.

21:31.340 --> 21:33.020
Suddenly, he's coming back to see us.

21:33.580 --> 21:34.500
I'm wondering

21:34.500 --> 21:36.470
if you can have your spirit

21:36.740 --> 21:38.100
stop my son from coming here

21:38.430 --> 21:39.710
and get him back to the Capital.

21:40.300 --> 21:41.230
I've heard Luda

21:41.230 --> 21:42.470
went to the Capital at ten

21:42.470 --> 21:43.780
and never came back.

21:44.390 --> 21:45.230
Why?

21:45.470 --> 21:46.390
Are you afraid

21:46.390 --> 21:47.820
he'll know about your evil deal?

21:48.710 --> 21:49.740
Or are you afraid

21:49.740 --> 21:50.580
to lose this son?

21:52.780 --> 21:53.710
Miss,

21:53.710 --> 21:54.990
you must be joking.

21:58.340 --> 21:59.300
We've been living here

21:59.300 --> 22:00.140
for a couple of days.

22:00.580 --> 22:01.430
So you go help him.

22:03.060 --> 22:03.900
But you...

22:04.150 --> 22:05.020
Don't worry about me.

22:15.230 --> 22:16.340
Thank you, Miss.

22:24.780 --> 22:26.060
I'd like to see

22:27.540 --> 22:28.670
what you and Song Xingyu

22:28.820 --> 22:29.990
are up to.

23:27.060 --> 23:27.900
Young man,

23:28.340 --> 23:29.750
fancy meeting you here.

23:40.910 --> 23:41.760
You know what?

23:41.770 --> 23:42.980
I got back from out of town

23:43.100 --> 23:44.580
and found a way to make a fortune.

23:45.910 --> 23:46.750
Tell me about it.

24:14.060 --> 24:15.340
- You...
- Simu is right.

24:16.060 --> 24:16.900
As long as we wait...

24:20.430 --> 24:21.780
You'll come on your own.

24:22.950 --> 24:23.910
I don't want this sword.

24:23.910 --> 24:24.870
I have to go now.

24:33.430 --> 24:38.500
Be careful with fire in dry weather.

24:42.780 --> 24:47.230
Be careful with fire in dry weather.

24:48.060 --> 24:51.820
(Young Priest Luda of the Chong court)

25:18.580 --> 25:19.420
Seventeen?

25:20.990 --> 25:21.830
It's you.

25:23.580 --> 25:24.470
Why are you like this?

25:26.260 --> 25:27.100
What a surprise.

25:27.910 --> 25:29.020
You know me, Young Priest.

25:29.870 --> 25:31.470
How come you suddenly showed up?

25:32.300 --> 25:33.140
To be honest,

25:33.950 --> 25:34.870
your father sent me

25:35.230 --> 25:36.540
to make you return to the Capital.

25:37.780 --> 25:38.950
You know my father?

25:40.870 --> 25:42.020
This is

25:42.740 --> 25:43.580
just his excuse

25:43.580 --> 25:44.440
to lure me away.

25:45.500 --> 25:46.340
He wants to kill

25:46.340 --> 25:47.180
my friend and me.

25:48.300 --> 25:49.230
Then let's hurry back.

25:54.740 --> 25:55.710
You believe me already?

25:56.100 --> 25:56.940
What if I lied?

25:57.470 --> 25:58.310
There's no evil

25:58.910 --> 25:59.750
in your eyes.

26:01.430 --> 26:02.300
Will your friend

26:02.710 --> 26:03.550
be all right?

26:06.390 --> 26:07.230
Don't worry.

26:07.910 --> 26:08.750
She's smart.

26:09.580 --> 26:10.420
She won't be fooled

26:11.340 --> 26:12.190
the same way again.

27:16.670 --> 27:17.510
Father.

27:19.870 --> 27:20.710
Mother.

27:22.990 --> 27:23.830
Look.

27:25.540 --> 27:26.740
Now I can

27:26.740 --> 27:27.780
hold the two of you

27:27.780 --> 27:28.620
with just one arm.

27:34.670 --> 27:36.670
You always said you loved me,

27:41.820 --> 27:43.780
but you both left me.

27:46.260 --> 27:47.870
I'm left all alone.

27:58.870 --> 27:59.710
Simu.

28:07.150 --> 28:07.990
Simu,

28:08.950 --> 28:09.790
I'm leaving.

28:10.950 --> 28:12.230
A mortal doesn't live forever.

28:13.150 --> 28:14.300
I can't stay any longer.

28:15.100 --> 28:15.940
Simu,

28:16.430 --> 28:17.300
I can't live

28:18.150 --> 28:19.230
without your mother.

28:20.500 --> 28:21.630
I must leave with her.

28:24.470 --> 28:25.580
Didn't you promise

28:25.580 --> 28:26.820
to live with me?

28:27.580 --> 28:29.060
Why did you break your promise too?

28:29.870 --> 28:30.870
Why did every one of you

28:30.870 --> 28:31.950
have to abandon me?

28:34.780 --> 28:36.500
I don't want to be alone.

28:39.500 --> 28:40.990
I just don't want that.

28:50.060 --> 28:50.900
Simu,

29:00.100 --> 29:01.500
you can leave with us.

29:02.710 --> 29:04.190
Death will end everything.

29:05.190 --> 29:06.740
There will be no more pain.

29:07.300 --> 29:08.140
When you're dead,

29:08.870 --> 29:10.430
the three of us will reunite.

29:49.910 --> 29:50.750
Stop acting.

29:52.870 --> 29:53.710
My parents

29:53.990 --> 29:55.020
only want me

29:55.020 --> 29:56.100
to live a good life.

30:08.230 --> 30:09.740
You failed to find my vital center,

30:11.230 --> 30:13.060
so you tried to kill me in my dream.

30:14.540 --> 30:15.780
Lord of Jiling Temple,

30:17.580 --> 30:19.230
you tried really hard.

31:04.670 --> 31:06.060
You're such a loyal servant.

31:07.440 --> 31:08.300
I guess Song Xingyu

31:08.300 --> 31:09.390
must have promised you

31:10.100 --> 31:11.150
that after killing me,

31:11.150 --> 31:12.430
he will become the Sovereign

31:12.950 --> 31:14.470
and give you all the glory and wealth

31:14.470 --> 31:15.310
in this world.

31:16.300 --> 31:17.430
But have you ever thought

31:17.430 --> 31:18.500
about what will happen

31:20.630 --> 31:21.780
if he fails?

31:38.260 --> 31:39.100
Song Xingyu,

31:40.230 --> 31:41.910
it's really not easy for me

31:42.470 --> 31:43.390
to get to see you.

31:55.950 --> 31:56.990
He Simu,

31:57.950 --> 31:59.630
you've fallen this far.

32:00.190 --> 32:01.540
Why are you still talking tough?

32:02.340 --> 32:04.300
You're greedy, short-sighted,

32:04.500 --> 32:05.540
reckless, and foolish.

32:06.190 --> 32:07.300
In the past 300 years,

32:07.740 --> 32:09.340
you haven't grown at all.

32:10.150 --> 32:10.990
You...

32:11.300 --> 32:13.230
Give me the Spirits Lantern!

32:14.820 --> 32:16.340
It's not with me.

32:16.870 --> 32:18.060
Even if I die,

32:18.540 --> 32:20.020
it won't take you as its master.

32:20.430 --> 32:21.270
Then...

32:21.820 --> 32:23.470
Go get the Lantern back.

32:24.150 --> 32:25.630
Now you have no spirit power

32:25.630 --> 32:26.670
and very little magic.

32:27.020 --> 32:28.500
If you can't get it back,

32:29.630 --> 32:30.470
I will...

32:32.230 --> 32:33.230
I will throw you

32:33.230 --> 32:34.230
into South Sea Ice Coffin

32:35.390 --> 32:36.710
and lock you up forever.

32:40.100 --> 32:41.470
I have a question.

32:42.430 --> 32:43.910
If I'm satisfied with your answer,

32:44.670 --> 32:45.910
I suppose I can give you

32:45.910 --> 32:46.780
the Lantern.

32:49.670 --> 32:51.100
Why do you want to be the Sovereign?

32:52.230 --> 32:53.430
In this world,

32:53.430 --> 32:54.470
every spirit wants that.

32:55.020 --> 32:56.390
The Sovereign can do anything

32:56.390 --> 32:57.630
and gets anything

32:57.630 --> 32:58.470
he or she wants.

32:58.950 --> 33:01.150
All the treasures in this world

33:01.870 --> 33:04.060
will belong to me.

33:05.260 --> 33:06.230
And then?

33:08.430 --> 33:10.060
Spirits can't feel or enjoy

33:10.060 --> 33:11.100
the sensual pleasures

33:11.630 --> 33:13.260
or luxuries.

33:14.150 --> 33:15.300
So what's the point

33:15.500 --> 33:16.630
of having them?

33:17.780 --> 33:19.500
If it's not a precious position,

33:20.910 --> 33:22.500
why do you refuse to give it up?

33:29.630 --> 33:31.150
I'm not satisfied with your answer.

33:32.230 --> 33:33.580
I won't give this position

33:34.300 --> 33:35.820
to someone I hate.

33:36.540 --> 33:37.990
In that case,

33:38.820 --> 33:40.950
I'll kill you and take it!

34:05.500 --> 34:06.910
You're back sooner than expected.

34:08.660 --> 34:10.220
I think I'm back at a perfect time.

34:16.790 --> 34:17.630
Luda?

34:24.830 --> 34:25.670
Father,

34:26.100 --> 34:26.940
what are you doing?

34:27.270 --> 34:28.500
He had a deal with a spirit

34:28.990 --> 34:30.870
in exchange for your family fortune

34:30.870 --> 34:32.140
and your rapid promotion.

34:32.660 --> 34:33.990
These years, all your siblings

34:33.990 --> 34:35.220
died at a young age

34:36.350 --> 34:37.620
just because his misdeeds

34:37.620 --> 34:38.620
backfired on him.

34:41.180 --> 34:42.020
Father.

34:43.540 --> 34:44.380
Is she

34:44.870 --> 34:45.710
telling the truth?

35:59.660 --> 36:01.140
Please spare me, sir.

36:23.830 --> 36:24.670
Treasure Vault.

36:24.870 --> 36:25.870
My... My treasures.

36:26.500 --> 36:28.470
My collections of over ten years.

36:31.990 --> 36:32.830
Father.

36:33.180 --> 36:34.900
It's all over.

36:35.170 --> 36:36.020
- Oh no.
- Father.

36:36.020 --> 36:36.860
All is lost.

36:38.140 --> 36:38.980
Father.

36:47.060 --> 36:47.900
Sorry.

36:48.390 --> 36:49.230
He slipped away.

36:50.180 --> 36:51.020
It's all right.

36:51.830 --> 36:52.750
Next time, he won't be

36:52.750 --> 36:53.660
so fortunate.

37:17.790 --> 37:18.630
Are you all right?

37:21.100 --> 37:22.310
What could go wrong with me?

37:26.310 --> 37:27.700
Why were you so obedient this time?

37:27.950 --> 37:29.700
You did what I told you to.

37:32.100 --> 37:33.100
I don't know your plan.

37:33.910 --> 37:34.750
So I believe

37:35.430 --> 37:36.790
I shouldn't cause you any trouble.

38:02.540 --> 38:03.830
You smell so good.

38:05.700 --> 38:06.540
In the dream

38:06.540 --> 38:07.470
Song Xingyu fabricated,

38:08.430 --> 38:09.540
I smelled the pleasant aroma

38:09.540 --> 38:10.950
from your scented pouch.

38:41.100 --> 38:44.190
♪Touched memories♪

38:45.750 --> 38:46.660
In that case,

38:48.390 --> 38:49.500
why not smell a little more?

38:50.790 --> 38:53.070
♪Sink into my heart♪

38:54.700 --> 38:55.700
And since that night,

38:56.620 --> 38:57.790
you've kept a straight face.

38:59.390 --> 39:00.230
I suspect

39:01.950 --> 39:03.270
you'll settle the score with me

39:04.470 --> 39:05.430
after your power's back.

39:09.430 --> 39:10.790
So I might as well be bolder.

39:13.070 --> 39:18.730
♪A lifetime is given
for a name to be remembered♪

39:19.300 --> 39:22.680
♪There are passions and pains♪

39:22.900 --> 39:25.540
♪Hope we'll experience them together♪

39:26.420 --> 39:32.590
♪Before we forget or grow apart♪

39:32.610 --> 39:33.490
Besides,

39:34.950 --> 39:36.390
when I was away from you...

39:36.740 --> 39:38.350
♪Grows dim and fades away♪

39:39.500 --> 39:40.390
I flattered myself

39:40.390 --> 39:41.310
and worried about you.

39:41.690 --> 39:43.140
♪I care for no one but you♪

39:43.140 --> 39:44.470
♪I'll come near and run to you♪

39:44.470 --> 39:45.660
So you know

39:48.310 --> 39:49.790
you always flatter yourself.

39:49.790 --> 39:51.080
♪Eternity and radiance♪

39:51.080 --> 39:53.870
♪Worth more than any barren land♪

39:54.120 --> 39:56.490
♪I might as well
spend the rest of my life♪

39:56.490 --> 40:00.600
♪Walking with you through eternity♪

40:15.880 --> 40:21.210
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:21.540 --> 40:25.790
♪Light encountered shadow♪

40:27.150 --> 40:32.520
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

40:32.820 --> 40:37.420
♪The unbreakable fate♪

40:38.510 --> 40:40.350
♪Suddenly cracked♪

40:52.560 --> 40:58.000
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

40:58.180 --> 41:02.510
♪Light encountered shadow♪

41:03.880 --> 41:09.270
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

41:09.500 --> 41:13.440
♪The unbreakable fate♪

41:15.210 --> 41:17.100
♪Suddenly cracked♪

41:19.760 --> 41:22.920
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

41:22.920 --> 41:25.450
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

41:25.450 --> 41:30.970
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

41:30.970 --> 41:34.210
♪Following fate's guidance♪

41:34.210 --> 41:39.070
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

41:39.410 --> 41:42.430
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

41:42.430 --> 41:45.250
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

41:45.510 --> 41:48.040
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

41:48.040 --> 41:53.460
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

41:53.630 --> 41:56.700
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

41:56.860 --> 42:01.760
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

42:01.970 --> 42:05.440
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
